Organization Strategy- Our organization strategy follows the best practices for reproducibility and understanding
 
-Raw and Processed Data- We have separated our raw data and processed data. This is essential for transparency and reproducibility in a workflow. Raw data represents the original dataset and by keeping a separate unchanged file ensures we have a trusted baseline and we can restart our analysis if needed. It also allows anyone else to start from the exact same dataset and run the scripts we created to receive the same product. It also makes clear what changes we made and our transformation process is clearly displayed. 
